rows.label: qev040403_MSG0001
rows.name:
Satsuuu! Where are yoooou? Yoyotsu tired of looking!
Also really hungry.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040403_SEL0011
rows.name: Tell Yoyotsu that Satsu has been found.

rows.label: qev040403_SEL0021
rows.name: Tell Yoyotsu that Satsu departed on a long journey.

rows.label: qev040403_MSG0003
rows.name:
Hearing that make Yoyotsu very relieved.
Also more hungry.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040403_MSG0004
rows.name: Yoyotsu ready to go home and eat with everybody.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040403_MSG0006
rows.name:
But Yoyotsu guess all we can do now is wish Satsu
luck in terribly uncertain future.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040403_MSG0007
rows.name: And eat his lunch every day.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040403_MSG0008
rows.name:
It pain Yoyotsu in heart, but Yoyotsu will eat lost
sibling's lunch until pain moves to gut.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040403_MSG0009
rows.name: ...Meh? Friend was joking? Satsu is back at caravan?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040403_MSG0010
rows.name:
Yoyotsu very happy to hear it!
...Except part where friend lied like jerk.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev040403_MSG0011
rows.name:
Now to head back home and celebrate by eating till
Yoyotsu burst![ST:wait ]
